description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I’m a 33 year old female, dating a 34 year old man. We met at our college homecoming 2 years ago and we didn’t know each other in college, but we found out we have a lot of mutual friends. He’s an Alpha man and he’s very active in the fraternity and he loves hanging with his fraternity brothers. I am a photographer and a lot of my clients are attractive, single women......................
